org.openstack4j.model.senlin

Interface ClusterPolicy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelEntity, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SenlinClusterPolicy

    public interface ClusterPolicy
extends ModelEntity
    This interface describes the getter-methods (and thus components) of a ClusterPolicy. All getters map to the possible return values of GET /v1/clusters/​{cluster_id}​/policies/​{policy_id}​
    Author:
    lion
    See Also:
    http://developer.openstack.org/api-ref-clustering-v1.html
